setDetails.setDescription: OLI is a digital asset index built to provide a one-stop-shop for newcomers to the crypto space with an offering of a risk-adjusted, highly-reputable basket of token. We aim to ensure everyone is exposed to the potential gains, education and development of the blockchain market
setDetails.managerDescription: The Outis Laymans Index is a risk-weighted index tracking the performance of some of the most quality, use-case specific Ethereum-based products on the market.
